title: Atlas of military history in RUSSIA (RUS)
description:
MILITARY HISTORY OF RUSSIA



1) text in russian  , year: 1946

2) 95% of the book are maps

3) you NEED being able to read "Berlin" or "Warsaw" in russian

4) the book runs from the vikings to the japan war of 1904

5) it seems a publication destined to the training of army officials



6) the ACCURACY of the information is not guaranteed!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!




7) the general outlook of the book: very good (red and blue arrows over black white).
